body:
as our internals change, sometimes we saw things like this happen as pypi does not properly clean things up. Could you Try the following:
```
pip uninstall tensorflow
rm -rf ~/anaconda3/lib/python3.6/site-packages/tensorflow
pip install tensorflow
```
